1
00:00:37,260 --> 00:00:37,939
Tuan Zhou.

2
00:00:37,940 --> 00:00:39,380
Ayo pergi. Buru-buru.

3
00:00:40,100 --> 00:00:41,499
Hati-hati, nona.

4
00:00:41,500 --> 00:00:42,860
Pergi. Cepat.

5
00:00:47,440 --> 00:00:52,160
=Gema Kota Gang=

6
00:00:59,080 --> 00:01:04,960
=Episode 11=
(Selama Anda Kembali)

7
00:01:15,420 --> 00:01:16,460
Tetap di sini.

8
00:01:28,380 --> 00:01:30,940
Jika mereka mengetahuinya
Shuyi tidak mati dalam api,

9
00:01:31,340 --> 00:01:32,660
akan ada operasi lain.

10
00:01:34,020 --> 00:01:36,060
Kota Shen

11
00:01:36,300 --> 00:01:37,900
tidak aman untuknya sekarang.

12
00:01:38,220 --> 00:01:40,300
Kami sudah mengaturnya
untuk meninggalkan Kota Gang.

13
00:01:41,820 --> 00:01:42,940
Kapan dia pergi?

14
00:01:43,340 --> 00:01:44,980
Pelayaran jam 2 pagi malam ini

15
00:01:45,940 --> 00:01:47,340
melalui jalur Xiangshao.

16
00:02:46,990 --> 00:02:52,780
♪Malam ini hujan turun pelan♪

17
00:02:54,060 --> 00:02:59,860
♪Memadukan dengan huruf yang belum dibaca
melayang di udara♪

18
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:05,950
♪Kau berbalik dan melihatku kembali♪

19
00:03:09,500 --> 00:03:11,059
Jembatan Pontoon No. 3 sedang ditutup.

20
00:03:11,060 --> 00:03:12,620
Bergerak lebih cepat.

21
00:03:13,900 --> 00:03:18,930
♪Rasanya jiwa kita selaras♪

22
00:03:20,470 --> 00:03:25,940
♪Masa lalu atau masa depan,
cinta melampaui ingatan♪

23
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:32,350
♪Saat kau memelukku, aku hancur♪

24
00:03:33,600 --> 00:03:39,550
♪Saat bintang mengalir,
takdir masih menahan momen ini♪

25
00:03:39,790 --> 00:03:46,710
♪Berapa banyak surat yang telah aku tulis
hanya untukmu?♪

26
00:03:46,730 --> 00:03:52,480
♪Kalau saja kamu benar-benar bisa mendengarnya
apa yang ingin hatiku katakan♪

27
00:03:53,160 --> 00:03:59,489
♪Mulai dari kehidupan ini dan seterusnya
tidak ada jarak yang bisa memisahkan kita♪

28
00:03:59,490 --> 00:04:02,389
♪Janji yang kita buat♪

29
00:04:02,390 --> 00:04:06,169
♪Akan menemukan caranya untuk dipenuhi
suatu hari♪

30
00:04:06,170 --> 00:04:12,699
♪Akhirnya, balasanmu yang terlambat tiba♪

31
00:04:12,700 --> 00:04:19,440
♪Akhirnya aku mendengar jawabanmu dengan jelas♪

32
00:04:20,740 --> 00:04:23,100
Pak, kami...

33
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:31,050
♪Selama kamu di sini, aku punya semuanya♪

34
00:04:31,230 --> 00:04:34,739
♪Seluruh alam semesta♪

35
00:04:34,740 --> 00:04:35,700
Ayo pergi.

36
00:05:03,100 --> 00:05:03,979
Tuan Shen.

37
00:05:03,980 --> 00:05:07,280
(Sekolah Peiwen, Buku Latihan Bahasa Mandarin)

38
00:05:08,380 --> 00:05:10,780
Ini adalah pekerjaan rumah hari ini
dinilai oleh Tuan Zhou.

39
00:05:10,860 --> 00:05:11,980
Pergi bermain.

40
00:05:19,140 --> 00:05:20,460
(Dia telah tiba di Kota Gang)

41
00:05:24,340 --> 00:05:25,900
(aman dan sehat.)

42
00:05:43,860 --> 00:05:44,980
Ada berita?

43
00:05:45,140 --> 00:05:47,060
Tidak ada apa pun dari Nona Lin.

44
00:05:47,260 --> 00:05:49,659
Sejak Tuan Zhou berkata

45
00:05:49,660 --> 00:05:51,659
dia kehilangan kontak dengannya,

46
00:05:51,660 --> 00:05:53,580
dia tidak datang ke kelas selama seminggu.

47
00:06:35,500 --> 00:06:36,859
Minta kapal kargo ke Kota Gang

48
00:06:36,860 --> 00:06:39,780
kirimkan surat ini kepada Shuyi
atas namamu.

49
00:06:39,860 --> 00:06:41,939
Rahasiakan identitasnya.

50
00:06:41,940 --> 00:06:43,060
Jangan mengekspos dia.

51
00:06:43,740 --> 00:06:44,860
Dipahami.

52
00:06:49,860 --> 00:06:51,459
Qianmo, aku di sini.

53
00:06:51,460 --> 00:06:52,700
saya di sini.

54
00:06:52,860 --> 00:06:53,739
Tuan Shen berkata

55
00:06:53,740 --> 00:06:55,379
kamu harus membawa kembali berita tentang Nona Lin.

56
00:06:55,380 --> 00:06:56,380
Baiklah.

57
00:06:56,660 --> 00:06:57,860
aku pergi.

58
00:07:00,780 --> 00:07:02,620
Pastikan Anda melakukannya!

59
00:07:04,300 --> 00:07:06,020
Anda harus menyampaikan kembali beritanya!

60
00:07:06,110 --> 00:07:07,250
Buru-buru.

61
00:07:07,540 --> 00:07:08,360
Datang.

62
00:08:10,060 --> 00:08:12,380
Saya kehilangan kontak dengan Tuan Zhou.

63
00:08:12,860 --> 00:08:16,180
Juga belum ada kabar dari Shuyi
di Kota Gang.

64
00:08:17,740 --> 00:08:19,420
Pergi ke sana secara langsung

65
00:08:19,940 --> 00:08:22,700
dan menyampaikan
hal penting ini padanya.

66
00:08:22,780 --> 00:08:24,020
Pak,

67
00:08:24,060 --> 00:08:25,900
situasinya tegang.

68
00:08:26,060 --> 00:08:28,220
Apakah kamu yakin tidak akan ikut denganku?

69
00:08:35,380 --> 00:08:37,500
Aku punya sesuatu yang lebih penting untuk dilakukan.

70
00:09:09,340 --> 00:09:10,620
Nyonya Liu.

71
00:09:10,700 --> 00:09:11,820
Anak laki-laki itu.

72
00:09:13,740 --> 00:09:14,499
Dimana Nona Lin?

73
00:09:14,500 --> 00:09:16,980
Dimana dia, Nyonya Liu?

74
00:09:17,260 --> 00:09:19,100
Apakah dia menerima surat itu?

75
00:09:21,460 --> 00:09:23,339
Katakan sesuatu, Nyonya Liu.

76
00:09:23,340 --> 00:09:25,300
Jawab aku.

77
00:09:26,980 --> 00:09:28,100
Nona Lin...

78
00:09:28,660 --> 00:09:30,580
Dia mengorbankan dirinya sendiri.

79
00:09:31,700 --> 00:09:33,300
Dikorbankan?

80
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:35,269
Cepat.

81
00:09:35,270 --> 00:09:36,390
Di sini.

82
00:09:36,860 --> 00:09:37,489
Buru-buru.

83
00:09:37,490 --> 00:09:38,579
Di sini.

84
00:09:38,580 --> 00:09:39,539
Tidak ada waktu, nona.

85
00:09:39,540 --> 00:09:40,860
Anda harus pergi sekarang.

86
00:09:41,550 --> 00:09:42,820
Nona, cepatlah.

87
00:09:45,540 --> 00:09:47,100
Pastikan ini sampai ke Shen Gu.

88
00:09:47,460 --> 00:09:48,580
Nona.

89
00:09:49,180 --> 00:09:50,179
- Pergi.
- Nona

90
00:09:50,180 --> 00:09:53,420
- Pergi.
- Merindukan!

91
00:09:53,500 --> 00:09:57,180
Merindukan!

92
00:09:57,900 --> 00:09:59,419
Berlari!

93
00:09:59,420 --> 00:10:00,740
Nona.

94
00:10:02,460 --> 00:10:05,140
Merindukan!

95
00:10:13,520 --> 00:10:17,760
(Daftar Nama)

96
00:10:36,740 --> 00:10:37,860
Nona...

97
00:10:38,700 --> 00:10:40,860
Dia menerima surat itu.

98
00:10:41,660 --> 00:10:44,459
Ini balasannya kepada Tuan Shen.

99
00:10:44,460 --> 00:10:45,739
(Kepada Shen Gu)

100
00:10:45,740 --> 00:10:49,860
Tapi dia mati melindungi kita.

101
00:10:52,920 --> 00:10:54,259
(Kepada Shen Gu)

102
00:10:54,260 --> 00:10:56,540
Nona...

103
00:10:58,100 --> 00:10:58,780
Tidak.

104
00:10:59,660 --> 00:11:01,099
Ini tidak benar.

105
00:11:01,100 --> 00:11:01,859
Kamu tidak bisa berbohong padaku

106
00:11:01,860 --> 00:11:04,180
hanya karena aku masih kecil.

107
00:11:05,900 --> 00:11:07,060
Qianmo,

108
00:11:07,860 --> 00:11:11,780
Nona Lin sudah pergi.

109
00:11:12,340 --> 00:11:15,180
Dia benar-benar pergi.

110
00:11:39,420 --> 00:11:41,059
Tambahan!

111
00:11:41,060 --> 00:11:45,380
Presiden Shen Gu dari Kota Shen
Kamar Dagang sudah mati!

112
00:11:45,540 --> 00:11:48,100
Shen Gu sudah mati!

113
00:11:50,620 --> 00:11:52,860
Shen Gu sudah mati!

114
00:11:58,500 --> 00:12:00,620
Presiden Kota Shen
Kamar Dagang.

115
00:12:00,700 --> 00:12:03,100
Hadiah 500 koin perak
untuk si pembunuh.

116
00:12:03,300 --> 00:12:04,820
Apa yang sedang kamu lakukan?

117
00:12:06,860 --> 00:12:08,020
Ada apa denganmu?

118
00:12:12,140 --> 00:12:14,180
Hai! Apa masalahmu?

119
00:12:18,660 --> 00:12:20,820
Jangan ambil barang-barangku!

120
00:12:20,980 --> 00:12:22,580
Jangan ambil giokku!

121
00:12:23,660 --> 00:12:25,259
Jangan sentuh barang-barangku!

122
00:12:25,260 --> 00:12:26,539
Jangan!

123
00:12:26,540 --> 00:12:27,619
TIDAK!

124
00:12:27,620 --> 00:12:32,839
♪Tapi aku ingin lebih
dari sekedar tatapan sekilas itu♪

125
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:34,179
(Presiden Shen Gu sudah meninggal)

126
00:12:34,180 --> 00:12:35,660
Kembalikan.

127
00:12:36,060 --> 00:12:37,180
Kembalikan.

128
00:12:37,500 --> 00:12:40,099
Itu tanda Tuan Shen untuk Nona Lin.

129
00:12:40,100 --> 00:12:41,980
Itu adalah batu giok pusaka
dari keluarga Shen.

130
00:12:43,260 --> 00:12:45,780
Kembalikan.

131
00:12:47,310 --> 00:12:52,149
♪Saat penyesalan mulai berbalik padamu
akan mendengar semuanya♪

132
00:12:52,150 --> 00:12:55,840
(Presiden Shen Gu sudah meninggal)

133
00:13:21,900 --> 00:13:23,780
Kita bisa menggantungkan pita merah

134
00:13:24,580 --> 00:13:25,780
